    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Describes videotape with a width of 3/4 inches (19.7mm). Used professionally for many years until more compact formats with better resolution appeared.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
